To Win Match With Handicap (3 way)
 
• Bets on the Draw With Handicap selection are considered winning bets if the number of goals for each team is equal after taking into account the selected handicap

• Bets on the Team to Win selection are considered winning bets if:
   - the final goal difference between the teams is strictly over the selected negative handicap value for the selected team (if level, bets will be losing)
   - the final goal difference between the teams is strictly under the selected positive handicap value for the selected team (if level, bets will be losing)

To Win 1st Half With Handicap (3 way)
 
• Bets on the Draw With Handicap selection are considered winning bets if the number of goals for each team is equal after taking into account the selected handicap

• Bets on the Team to Win selection are considered winning bets if:
   - the final goal difference between the teams is strictly over the selected negative handicap value for the selected team (if level, bets will be losing)
   - the final goal difference between the teams is strictly under the selected positive handicap value for the selected team (if level, bets will be losing)
